        <a name="systemRequirements"></a>
        <h2>System requirements</h2>

        <p>Collector requires certain device requirements to run, as well as having requirements on the data that is used within the application. Collector is supported in a number of languages.</p>


        <h3>Data requirements</h3>
        <p>To use your data in Collector, you must use ArcGIS.com or Portal for ArcGIS version 2.1 or later.</p>


        <h3>Device requirements</h3>
        <table><tr><td valign="top" width="250px;"><h4 class="icon-android">Android</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Android 4.0 (Ice Cream Sandwich)<br/>or higher operating system</li>
          <li>Armv7 processor</li>
          <li>OpenGL ES 2.0 support</li>
        </ul></td>
        <td valign="top"><h4 class="icon-apple">iPad</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>iOS 5 or higher</li>
        </ul></td><tr></table>


        <h3>Supported languages</h3>
        <p>Arabic, Danish, Dutch, English, Estonian (Android only), French, German, Hebrew, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Latvian (Android only), Lithuanian (Android only), Norwegian, Polish, Portuguese (Brazil), Portuguese (Portugal), Romanian, Russian, Simplified Chinese, Spanish, and Swedish.</p>
        <p>The language used by the application is determined by your phone's language setting.</p>






